The magnitude 6 . 6 quake hit a remote mountainous area of southwestern China ' s Sichuan province at 8 : 02 a . m . ( 0002 GMT ), close to where an earthquake killed almost 70 , 000 people in 2008 . The quake struck in Lushan county , near the city of Ya ' an , at a depth of 12 km ( 7 . 5 miles ), the U . S . Geological Survey said .